table_description: AWS ServiceQuotas Service Quota Change Request

columns.name: status
columns.description: The state of the quota increase request.

columns.name: quota_arn
columns.description: The arn of the service quota.

columns.name: desired_value
columns.description: The increased value for the quota.

columns.name: created
columns.description: The date and time when the quota increase request was received and the case ID was created.

columns.name: global_quota
columns.description: Indicates whether the quota is global.

columns.name: last_updated
columns.description: The date and time of the most recent change.

columns.name: requester
columns.description: The IAM identity of the requester.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: The list of tags associated with the change request.
